#-----------------------
# Arcane Arranger
#-----------------------

###Block:Arcane Arranger
# Ability Name		Unique Key					Category of Ability		Type										Define				Description
Expert in Your Field	KEY:Arcane Arranger ~ Expert in Your Field	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Arcane Arranger Class Feature.Class Feature							DESC:You are considered a master of connections, such that your reputation precedes you in your dealings with others. You gain a circumstance bonus equal to your Reputation bonus when making skill checks that are directly involved with Gather Information and Diplomacy skills. In addition, your may add your Reputation bonus on Wealth checks for new purchases.
False Allegiance	KEY:Arcane Arranger ~ False Allegiance		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Arcane Arranger Class Feature.Class Feature							DESC:You fit in with whatever group you choose to be with. You can successfully emulate an allegiance you know about. You gain the +2 circumstance bonus on Charisma-based skills when dealing with an individual of the same allegiance.  The allegiance and its bonus is considered in effect until a check is failed, at which point the false allegiance is revealed.  Supernatural and spell-like abilities that determine allegiance are not affected by your false allegiance ability.
Pack Rat		KEY:Arcane Arranger ~ Pack Rat			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Arcane Arranger Class Feature.Class Feature							DESC:You are considered to have considerable material resources either at hand or easily and cheaply acquired. When making a Wealth check to determine if a particular item is "at hand," add your Arcane Arranger class levels as a circumstance bonus.
Shadow Resources	KEY:Arcane Arranger ~ Shadow Resources		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Arcane Arranger Class Feature.Class Feature							DESC:You are well-enough wired into the social system to be able to get the names and numbers of individuals with particular abilities and talents. Even if away from your home stomping ground a phone call can produce a contact with the needed resource. Make a level check, adding all Arcane Arranger levels and any levels of Charismatic Hero. &nl;The difficulty of this task is based on how common the required abilities are: &nl;Common Skill (Ride, Pilot, Treat Injury) DC 10 &nl;Uncommon Skill (subgroups of other skills such as Knowledge (arcane lore) or Craft (structural)) DC 15 &nl;Rare Skill (skills available for a particular class-Spellcraft, Psicraft, Use Magic Device) DC 20 &nl;Specific Feat DC 20 &nl;Class Feature (spellcasting, turn undead, psionics) DC 20 &nl;Specific Combination of Skills, Feats, and Abilities (someone with Knowledge (business) and the ability to cast the auguryspell) DC 25 &nl;Finding someone willing to perform activities secretly or illegally DC +5 &nl;Finding someone with a specific level of ability Add desired ranks to DC A successful check indicates that the individual is available, and you know about him. It does not guarantee the character contacted will be willing to perform the requested service-the party requesting the service must still negotiate for that person's services. &nl;An unsuccessful check means that no such individual is immediately known or available to you. This does not negate trying again for a different skill, nor from trying to locate a skill resource through more traditional methods. The resource you know about will have total ranks in the needed skill of at least your total character level +3.
Up My Sleeve		KEY:Arcane Arranger ~ Up My Sleeve		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Arcane Arranger Class Feature.Class Feature.Supernatural	DEFINE:ArcaneArrangerLVL|0	DESC:You gain the supernatural ability to pull a specific item out of thin air. As a move action, you may cause	DESC: any item currently in your possession (with a size no greater than Small)|PREVARLT:ArcaneArrangerLVL,10	DESC: a single object currently in your possession of up to Large size or up to three objects of up to Small size (each of which may be retrieved individually)|PREVARGTEQ:ArcaneArrangerLVL,10	DESC: to disappear into an extra-dimensional space. The item becomes impossible to detect by any means, however detect magical aura spells will reveal a moderate magical aura around the hand that last held the item. As a move action, you can cause any of the items to reappear in your hand.	DESC:You may only hide one item at a time in this fashion.|PREVARLT:ArcaneArrangerLVL,10
Word on the Street	KEY:Arcane Arranger ~ Word on the Street	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Arcane Arranger Class Feature.Class Feature							DESC:You filter information constantly and remember everything. Through regular contacts, gossip, internet chats, and other situations, you have a deep knowledge of everyday things. You can make a Gather Information check on general or specific information instantaneously, and spend only an hour making a Gather Information check for restricted information. Retries may be made under normal rules.  Protected information still requires 1d4+1 hours for a check.  The purchase DC for using Gather Information is reduced by 10.


