# Archaic Weaponsmaster
#-----------------------

###Block:Archaic Weaponsmaster
# Ability Name		Unique Key						Category of Ability		Type									Define				Description																																										Modify VAR							Benefits
Expert in Your Field	KEY:Archaic Weaponsmaster ~ Expert in Your Field	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Archaic Weaponsmaster Class Feature.Class Feature					DESC:You are considered to be a master of your particular weapon.  You gain a circumstance bonus equal to your Reputation bonus on skill checks that are directly involved with your knowledge and proficiency with the weapon. Such skills would include applicable Knowledge skills, as well as such social skills such as Intimidate and Bluff.									BENEFIT:At 5th level, the Archaic Weaponsmaster is considered to be a master of her particular weapon, whether this is as a scholar with a detailed knowledge of the weaponâ€™s history, or as a practitioner, such as a professional archer. Starting with 5th level, the Archaic Weaponsmaster gains a circumstance bonus equal to her Reputation bonus on skill checks that are directly involved with her knowledge and proficiency with the weapon. Such skills would include applicable Knowledge skills, as well as such social skills as Intimidate and Bluff.
Imbue Weapon		KEY:Archaic Weaponsmaster ~ Imbue Weapon		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Archaic Weaponsmaster Class Feature.Class Feature	DEFINE:ImbueWeaponBonus|0	DESC:Treat any archaic weapon you have Weapon Focus with as if it had a +%1 for overcoming damage reduction.|ImbueWeaponBonus																												BONUS:VAR|ImbueWeaponBonus|(ArchaicWeaponsmasterLVL+4)/6	BENEFIT:The Archaic Weaponsmaster may treat any archaic weapon she wields and has Weapon Focus with as a +%1 magic weapon for purposes of striking creatures with damage reduction. This does not grant the weapon a +%1 bonus, but only allows it to circumvent damage reduction.|ImbueWeaponBonus
Quick Weapon Draw	KEY:Archaic Weaponsmaster ~ Quick Weapon Draw		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Archaic Weaponsmaster Class Feature.Class Feature					DESC:You gain the ability to draw your weapon as a free action. This applies only to the weapons for which you have Weapon Specialization.																																		BENEFIT:At 4th level, the Archaic Weaponsmaster gains the ability to draw her weapon as a free action. This applies only to the weapons for which the Archaic Weaponsmaster has Weapon Specialization.
Weapon Stun		KEY:Archaic Weaponsmaster ~ Weapon Stun			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Archaic Weaponsmaster Class Feature.Class Feature					DESC:Deal nonlethal damage with any weapon for which you have weapon specialisation, without taking the -4 penalty on attack rolls.																																			BENEFIT:At 7th level, the Archaic Weaponsmaster can use his or her weapon to deal nonlethal damage, without taking the -4 penalty on attack rolls. The Archaic Weaponsmaster must have Weapon Specialization in the weapon to use it in this fashion.


